            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Withdrawal of Major Anderson</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Anderson</ln>
                        <pf>Major</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>SS learned from an article in the Vindicator that Anderson has declined his
                    nomination by the Democrats. Wonders who they will choose now, says that
                    Vindicators indignation toward the SS is misplaced.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
