                        <ln>Fontaine</ln>
                        <pf>Col.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Calls readers attention to Fontaine's letter in col. 4. Reduction in
                    railroad rates makes production and export of produce more profitable.</summary>
            </div>
