                    <name>
                        <ln>Fontaine</ln>
                        <pf>F.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Extract of minutes of Board of Directors Meeting of Virginia Central
                    Railroad, 3/30/57. More cars for cattle, lower transport rates for hay and
                    potatoes.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Colonizing Virginia</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Report on a group from Mass supposedly planning to colonize eastern
                    Virginia. SS thinks its a hoax.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>The Crops</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The dry winter didn't look promising for the wheat crop, but some recent
                    rain and sunshine should result in an abundant harvest.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="l">
                <column>7</column>
                <head>For the Spectator</head>
